**COPPA Compliance**: All features must comply with Children's Online Privacy Protection Rule
**No Personal Data**: Never collect personal information from minors under any circumstances
**Data Minimization**: Only collect data absolutely necessary for game functionality
**Security-First**: All decisions prioritize security over convenience or performance
**Environment Variables**: All secrets must be stored in environment variables, never hardcoded
**Input Validation**: Validate all user inputs server-side to prevent injection attacks
**Path Security**: Use secure path validation for all file operations
**Rate Limiting**: Implement per-user and per-endpoint rate limiting
**Privacy by Design**: Build privacy considerations into every feature from the start
